OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1773399918
OL,3,CMLAs to get #14k pay rise in weeks
OL,5,FA 27% pay rise for MLAs at Stormont
OL,6,Fhas been confirmed by an independent
OL,7,Fbody despite an "overwhelmingly
OL,8,Fcritical" public response.
OL,10,FSinn Fein leader Mary Lou McDonald
OL,11,Fdescribed the pay increase as
OL,12,F"absolutely excessive" while DUP
OL,13,Fleader Gavin Robinson said he did not
OL,14,Fthink "it plays well at all".
OL,16,FPay for representatives at Stormont
OL,17,Fwill rise from #53,000 to #67,200 per
OL,18,Fyear, the Independent Remuneration
OL,19,FBoard has ruled following a two-week
OL,20,Fconsultation involving MLAs and the
OL,21,FAssembly Commission.
OL,26,@oD@QOUpD@IO]tD@AOUtD@VO]vD@GOUvD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1773399918
OL,3,CMLAs to get #14k pay rise in weeks
OL,5,FThe uplift comes alongside the
OL,6,Fintroduction of new financial
OL,7,Fsanctions meaning if an Executive is
OL,8,Fnot formed after an election, MLA
OL,9,Fsalaries would be reduced by 10% after
OL,10,Fsix weeks, a further 10% at 12 weeks
OL,11,Fand another 10% after week 18.
OL,13,FAlan Lowry, chairman of the board,
OL,14,Fsaid they are "required to balance a
OL,15,Fnumber of issues ` the importance and
OL,16,Fcomplexity of an MLA's role, the
OL,17,Ffinancial viability of a political
OL,18,Fcareer and the levels of pay for
OL,19,Fpolitical representatives in peer
OL,20,Fparliaments".
OL,26,@vD@OOU|D@LO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1773399918
OL,3,CMLAs to get #14k pay rise in weeks
OL,5,FHe acknowledged that the public
OL,6,Fresponse had been "overwhelmingly
OL,7,Fcritical", with many "saying that this
OL,8,Fis not the right time to be tackling
OL,9,Fthis issue".
OL,11,F"It is clear that the system for
OL,12,Fconsidering MLA pay has not been
OL,13,Fworking properly for 10 years, and any
OL,14,Fdelay would only further exacerbate
OL,15,Fthe situation," he said.
OL,17,FSpeaking at the Culloden Hotel after a
OL,18,Fmeeting with UK Prime Minister Sir
OL,19,FKeir Starmer, Ms McDonald said "the
OL,20,Frise in MLAs' pay should be consistent
OL,21,Fwith public sector pay".
OL,26,@nD@SOUoD@IO]oD@VOUqD@KO]sD@AOUwD@OO]{D@
OL,26,A`OU}D@WO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1773399918
OL,3,CMLAs to get #14k pay rise in weeks
OL,5,F"So we have said that, this is an
OL,6,Findependent panel that is now
OL,7,Fdeliberating on this matter, they will
OL,8,Fmake their decision known, but we have
OL,9,Fmade our position absolutely crystal
OL,10,Fclear on this matter," she said.
OL,12,FShe added: "Any talk of #14,000 is
OL,13,Fabsolutely excessive, and I understand
OL,14,Fwhy that is deeply frustrating and
OL,15,Fannoying for the general public, but I
OL,16,Falso know in circumstances where the
OL,17,Fcost of home heating oil has rocketed
OL,18,Fby 60% in a matter of weeks, the issue
OL,19,Ffor people is how to keep their homes
OL,20,Fwarm."
OL,26,@mD@AOUrD@VO]tD@LOU|D@FO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1773399918
OL,3,CMLAs to get #14k pay rise in weeks
OL,5,FMr Robinson said he believes "it's
OL,6,Ftotally inappropriate that politicians
OL,7,Fshould have a role in setting their
OL,8,Fpay, a role in determining their value
OL,9,For worth".
OL,11,F"This independent process was
OL,12,Festablished for the very reason of
OL,13,Fensuring that politicians do not have
OL,14,Fthat role, and just as I personally
OL,15,Fhave no role in determining my pay in
OL,16,FWestminster, then, nor should assembly
OL,17,Fmembers, so that decision has been
OL,18,Ftaken," he said.
OL,26,@mD@^OUqD@IO]sD@AOUzD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1773399918
OL,3,CMLAs to get #14k pay rise in weeks
OL,5,FAlliance Party leader Naomi Long said
OL,6,Fshe was not going to defend "an
OL,7,Funconscionably high rise".
OL,9,F"I understand the rationale that the
OL,10,Findependent review body had in terms
OL,11,Fof wanting to peg the assembly and
OL,12,Fexecutive against other legislatures
OL,13,Fin these islands, but the reality is,
OL,14,Fother legislatures in these islands
OL,15,Ffunction and deliver and we struggle
OL,16,Fto do either of those things a lot of
OL,17,Fthe time," she said.
OL,19,F"So I think until we get that sorted,
OL,20,Fthis kind of pay rise is not
OL,21,Facceptable."
OL,26,@nD@]OUoD@YO]qD@AOUyD@JO]{D@AOU}D@LO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1773399918
OL,3,CMLAs to get #14k pay rise in weeks
OL,5,FShe added: "I don't believe, at a time
OL,6,Fwhen I had to wait until Christmas to
OL,7,Fbe able to institute pay for police
OL,8,Fofficers, that I should be seeing a
OL,9,F27% pay increase.
OL,11,F"It just doesn't make sense, and it's
OL,12,Fnot helpful.
OL,14,F"It's not helpful to political
OL,15,Fcredibility, it's not helpful to
OL,16,Frelationships and respect for
OL,17,Fdemocratic institutions, and I think
OL,18,Fit's completely misguided."
OL,26,@mD@LOUsD@AOUvD@AOUzD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1773399918
OL,3,CMLAs to get #14k pay rise in weeks
OL,5,FUUP leader Jon Burrows said he
OL,6,Funderstands the public frustration and
OL,7,Fthat the "performance of Stormont is
OL,8,Fnot good enough".
OL,10,FHe added: "We've taken a strategic,
OL,11,Fethical decision to have no input into
OL,12,Four pay, that's what other employees
OL,13,Fdeal with, and whether the independent
OL,14,Fbody recommended our payment up or
OL,15,Fdown, we will stay out of that and
OL,16,Fkeep doing our job."
OL,18,FSDLP leader Claire Hanna said her
OL,19,Fparty "don't believe that you can
OL,20,Freform any job with such a pay bump
OL,21,Fwithout key performance indicators".
OL,26,@oD@JOUpD@PO]rD@KOUxD@TO]{D@GOU}D@cO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/9
