OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1773399918
OL,3,CMLAs to get #14k pay rise in weeks
OL,5,FReiterating her party's commitment to
OL,6,Freforming political institutions she
OL,7,Fsaid: "The potential to increase MLA
OL,8,Fpay is exactly the right time to get
OL,9,Fthe mechanisms in place that mean that
OL,10,Fpeople can start to believe in
OL,11,FStormont again, because the visceral
OL,12,Fpublic reaction is precisely because
OL,13,Fpeople feel that Stormont doesn't work
OL,14,Ffor them."
